Package: OptimalFactor
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Factor Analysis with EFA-Boosting Algorithm
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-01-20
Authors@R:
    person("Jose", "Ventura-Leon",
           email = "jventuraleon@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2996-4244"))
Description: Provides an advanced iterative optimization algorithm for
    Exploratory Factor Analysis (EFA) using a machine-learning inspired
    boosting approach. The package implements adaptive composite fit indices
    with weights that adjust dynamically based on degrees of freedom and sample
    size following Kenny, Shi, and Savalei (2022) recommendations. Features
    include automatic detection and removal of problematic items (Heywood cases,
    cross-loadings, low loadings), greedy and global search strategies for
    optimal item selection, interfactor correlation verification, and optional
    AI-assisted conceptual analysis of removed items using GPT models. Supports
    ordinal data with WLSMV estimation and various rotation methods.
